rules.expr:
clamp_max(
  (
    (sum(sum_over_time({__name__="^cx_service_catalog_apdex_satisfied.+?_cx_docs_total$_cx_docs_total", cx_source="spans2metrics", }[60s])) by (service) or on () vector(0))
    + 
    (sum(sum_over_time({__name__="^cx_service_catalog_apdex_tolerating.+?_cx_docs_total$_cx_docs_total" ,cx_source="spans2metrics", }[60s])) by (service) / 2 or on () vector(0))
  ) 
  / sum(sum_over_time(cx_service_catalog_duration_update_cx_docs_total{cx_source="spans2metrics",spanKind=~"server|consumer"}[60s])) by (service)
  ,1) 

or

 clamp_max(
  (
    (sum(sum_over_time({__name__="cx_service_catalog_apdex_satisfied_cx_docs_total", cx_source="spans2metrics", service_name!~"cartservice|currencyservice|emailservice|FetchCustomerHistoryFromRDS-faas|FetchCustomerHistoryFromRDS-faasavion|frontend|productcatalogservice|web-app"}[60s])) by (service) or on () vector(0))
    + 
    (sum(sum_over_time({__name__="cx_service_catalog_apdex_tolerating_cx_docs_total" ,cx_source="spans2metrics", service_name!~"cartservice|currencyservice|emailservice|FetchCustomerHistoryFromRDS-faas|FetchCustomerHistoryFromRDS-faasavion|frontend|productcatalogservice|web-app"}[60s])) by (service) / 2 or on () vector(0))
  ) 
  / sum(sum_over_time(cx_service_catalog_duration_update_cx_docs_total{cx_source="spans2metrics",spanKind=~"server|consumer",service_name!~"cartservice|currencyservice|emailservice|FetchCustomerHistoryFromRDS-faas|FetchCustomerHistoryFromRDS-faasavion|frontend|productcatalogservice|web-app"}[60s])) by (service)
  ,1)
